    <li>task.parcel_legal_description</li>
    <li>task.payoff_amount_string</li>
    <li>task.beneficiary_name</li>
    <li>task.beneficiary_account</li>
    <li>task.lender.xxxx</li>
    <li>task.recorded_on</li>
    <li>task.docs_delivered_on</li>
    <li>task.reconveyance_filed</li>
    <li>task.first_notice_sent_on</li>
    <li>task.second_notice_sent_on</li>
    <li>task.last_search_at</li>
  </ul>

  <h5>User <small>(current logged-in user)</small></h5>
  <ul class="no-bullet code code-labels">
    <li>user.name</li>
    <li>user.email</li>
  </ul>

  <h5>State Object Reference</h5>
  <p>A state is a child of something else:</p>
  <ul class="no-bullet code code-labels">
    <li>job.state.name</li>
    <li>job.state.abbreviation</li>
    <li>job.state.counties</li>
  </ul>

  <h5>County Object Reference</h5>
  <p>A county is a child of something else:</p>
  <ul class="no-bullet code code-labels">
    <li>job.county.name</li>
    <li>job.county.state.xxxx</li>
  </ul>

  <h5>Lender Object Reference</h5>
  <p>A lender is a child of the task:</p>
  <ul class="no-bullet code code-labels">
    <li>task.lender.name</li>
    <li>task.lender.average_days_to_complete</li>
  </ul>

  <h5>Client Object Reference</h5>
  <p>A client is a child of the job:</p>
  <ul class="no-bullet code code-labels">
    <li>job.client.name</li>
    <li>job.client.website</li>
    <li>job.client.billing_address</li>
    <li>job.client.billing_city</li>
    <li>job.client.billing_state.xxxxx</li>
    <li>job.client.billing.zipcode</li>
  </ul>

  <h5>Requestor Object Reference</h5>
  <p>A requestor is a child of the job:</p>
  <ul class="no-bullet code code-labels">
    <li>job.requestor.name</li>
    <li>job.requestor.email</li>
  </ul>

</div>

